In OpenTTD, '''candyfloss'''  is grown on trees in the [[en/toyland|toyland climate]]. The candyfloss should be transported to the [[en/Manual/Base Set/Economy/Sweet Factory]] to be made into sweets. Also, the candyfloss is transported in [[en/Manual/Base Set/Vehicles/Candyfloss Trucks|hopper trucks]] to it's destination.